title: Saturday Special - Colin talks with Clay Travis of Fox Sports Radio and FS1
itunes:title: Saturday Special - Colin talks with Clay Travis of Fox Sports Radio and FS1
description:
Colin talks with Clay Travis of Fox Sports Radio and FS1 about the Democratic debates and the upcoming election. They also discuss why the NBA Ratings are down and what is the most important issue in the NFL CBA negotiations.
